  "diagram_type": "pie",
  "code": "classDiagram\n    class ConnectFour {\n        -Board board\n        -GameState gameState\n        -Player currentPlayer\n        -ConnectFourObserver observer\n        +ConnectFour(int rows, int cols, Player player1, Player player2)\n        +getBoard() Board\n        +getGameState() GameState\n        +getCurrentPlayer() Player\n        +makeMove(Move move) boolean\n        +getPossibleMoves() List~Move~\n        +registerObserver(ConnectFourObserver observer) void\n        -notifyObserver() void\n        +toString() String\n        +main(String[] args) void\n    }\n\n    class Board {\n        -final int ROWS\n        -final int COLS\n        -Column[] columns\n        +Board()\n        +Board(int rows, int cols)\n        +dropPiece(int columnIndex, Piece piece) int\n        +isFull() boolean\n        +getRows() int\n        +getCols() int\n        +getColumn(int colIndex) Column\n        +getCell(int row, int col) Cell\n        +getPiece(int row, int col) Piece\n    }\n\n    class Column {\n        -Cell[] cells\n        +Column(int rows)\n        +addPiece(Piece piece) int\n        +isFull() boolean\n        +getCells() Cell[]\n        +getCell(int row) Cell\n    }\n\n    class Cell {\n        -Piece piece\n        +Cell()\n        +isEmpty() boolean\n        +setPiece(Piece piece) void\n        +getPiece() Piece\n        +toSymbol() BoardSymbol\n    }\n\n    class Player {\n        -String name\n        -Piece piece\n        +Player(String name, Piece piece)\n        +getName() String\n        +getPiece() Piece\n    }\n\n    class Move {\n        -final int column\n        -final Piece piece\n        +Move(int column, Piece piece)\n        +getColumn() int\n        +getPiece() Piece\n        +toString() String\n    }\n\n    class WinChecker {\n        -final Board board\n        +WinChecker(Board board)\n        +checkWin(Piece piece) boolean\n        -checkHorizontal(Piece piece) boolean\n        -checkVertical(Piece piece) boolean\n        -checkDiagonal(Piece piece) boolean\n    }\n\n    class ConnectFourException {\n        +ConnectFourException(String message)\n    }\n\n    class Piece {\n        <<enumeration>>\n        RED\n        YELLOW\n        +toSymbol() String\n    }\n\n    class GameState {\n        <<enumeration>>\n        IN_PROGRESS\n        RED_WINS\n        YELLOW_WINS\n        DRAW\n    }\n\n    class BoardSymbol {\n        <<enumeration>>\n        EMPTY\n        RED\n        YELLOW\n        -final String symbol\n        +BoardSymbol(String symbol)\n        +getSymbol() String\n    }\n\n    class ConnectFourObserver {\n        <<interface>>\n        +updateBoard() void\n    }\n\n    %% Relationships\n    ConnectFour --> Board : contains\n    ConnectFour --> GameState : uses\n    ConnectFour --> Player : has current\n    ConnectFour --> Move : uses\n    ConnectFour --> WinChecker : creates\n    ConnectFour --> ConnectFourObserver : observes\n    ConnectFour --> ConnectFourException : throws\n\n    Board --> Column : contains array of\n    Column --> Cell : contains array of\n    Cell --> Piece : contains\n    Cell --> BoardSymbol : returns\n\n    Player --> Piece : has\n    Move --> Piece : contains\n\n    WinChecker --> Board : analyzes\n    WinChecker --> Piece : checks for\n\n    ConnectFourException --|> Exception : extends",
